# Privacy Policy for JeJu: Stories for Kids

Last updated: January 17, 2024

## 1. Introduction
JeJu: Stories for Kids app respects and protects user privacy. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect user data.

## 2. Data Collection
### 2.1 Microphone Permission (RECORD_AUDIO)
- The app uses the microphone **solely** for speech-to-text functionality.
- We do not store any audio recordings.
- Voice processing occurs in real-time.
- Audio data is not saved or transmitted to servers.

## 3. Data Usage
- Speech-to-text conversion is used only for app interaction.
- Converted text is used locally within the app.
- We do not share any data with third parties.

## 4. Security
- We do not store any audio data.
- Processing occurs locally on the user's device.
- We use standard Android system security measures.

## 5. User Rights
Users have the right to:
- Disable microphone access in system settings
- Delete the app and all associated data

## 6. Contact
For privacy-related questions, please contact:
support@jeju.app 
